1... Bb4+ { Stockfish's fave. 🤓🐠 } { [%csl Gc3][%cal Gc2c3] } 2. c3 dxc3 { Ignore this and castle! } { [%csl Gg1][%cal Ge1g1] } 3. O-O cxb2 { PLEASE play the correct move here. No hints. 🤫 } 4. Bxb2 { [%csl Rg7][%cal Rb2g7] } 4... Nf6 { Kick that Horsey! 🥾 } { [%csl Ge5][%cal Ge4e5] } 5. e5 Ng4 { Do it again! 🥾 } 6. h3 Nh6 { In this position, black's pieces are disoriented and not working together. Are pieces and position are superior. +1.0. Great work! 😄 } { [%csl Rg7,Rf7,Rg5,Re5][%cal Rb2g7,Rc4f7,Rf3g5,Rf3e5] } *


